comments: She\'s a fantastic teacher and the class is fun cause she like to make jokes.

Her test comes from homework material so if you do your homework, you will definitely pass. also she doesnt like for you to tell her that you feel like you are going to fail. she likes positive attitude
If you read the book, you\'ll do well in this class.
